               <head>Or ha-levanah by Isaac ben Solomon</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85009019" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Astronomical work.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="91v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/43825362">Isaac ben Solomon, Karaite, 1755-1826</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/43825362">יצחק בן שלמה, הקראי</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Or ha-levanah</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אור הלבנה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A treatise on the mode of fixing and consecrating the New Moon, including many calendrical tables. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Two additional pieces are appended: a treatise on the manner of harmonizing the solar year with the lunar year, dated <date calendar="Hebrew">5591</date> (<date calendar="Gregorian">1831</date>), and additional piece of establishing the New Moon, based on Isaac ben Solomon's Or ha-levanah. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <colophon xml:lang="he">והשלמתיו יום ששי לסדר מטות מסעי כח תמוז בשנת <date calendar="Hebrew">והי"ה או"ר הלבנ"ה</date> לפ"ק: פה <name type="place">גוזלווא</name> יע"א. <locus n="87v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     </colophon>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
